title: Kunara Cafe
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Western, Juice bar, Take-out, Catering, Australian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. The standard vegan items are muffins and a braised bean dish for breakfast; at lunch nachos and veggie burger and fries (specify vegan). There are also various items in the display cabinet. Range of smoothies and sweet treats. Does not use microwave. Kitchen closes at 2.30pm.
